<p>There is not only Blighted plant life standing in your way, but Golems! These are mechanical bodies which humans transferred their souls into.</p>
<p>The game also features a spin on the typical real-time action RPG with Blooming Arts, which slows down the gameplay and allows you to perform a selection of special attacks. This, as shown in the presentation, allows for a large variety of gameplay styles.</p>
<p>The game can be wishlisted now, and will be available on PC, Xbox Series X/S, and PS5. If you want to see everything revealed at the Xbox Developer Direct, <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/will-fable-steal-the-show-at-tonights-xbox-developer-direct-join-us-here-to-discuss-everything-announced-as-it-happens">check out our live blog here</a>!</p>

